title: Erectile Dysfunction and Heart Disease: What’s the Connection?
description: Your heart and blood vessels are critical when it comes to erections. After all, erections are achieved when the blood vessels in the penis open up, which allows more blood to rush into the penis leading to an erection. If that blood flow is interrupted, blocked, or slowed down for any reason, you might not be able to get or keep an erection.
